descript.abstract: These are summarized data from the CFIS data base. They represent commercial landing reciepts from southern California ports. Each block is attributed with the average catch of a number of species catagories from 1998 through 2007. This data extract was made by Gerry Kobylinski and handed off to the DFG GIS lab in May of 2008.
